Package tacTile.net

Class Summary
TouchAPI TouchAPI is an addition to the Processing Libraries written so Processing applications could communicate with the TacTile.
Tac Tile is a Multi-touch table begin researched at the Electronic Visualization Lab at the University of Illinois at Chicago.
Touches Touches is essentially a data structure that stores information about a touch:
Time Stamp:
The time that the touch Occurred.
